{"tid":123822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"次次係OK 7仔啲雪糕櫃搵完一輪，都會好失望咁走","createTime":"2017-02-17T06:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T06:55:59.000Z","uid":79744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb07820cacb9c44b2510de5ef9cdd6b979dab48c","tid":123822,"uid":79744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"價錢牌就多，但根本成個雪櫃有既雪糕雪條種類得好少<br />\n淨係HaagenDaz Drayers、同十幾廿蚊既韓國雪糕/條都佔左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼左特價嗰啲就一定次次未天黑就冇哂<br />\n<br />\n次次望完價錢牌，<br />\n之後搵來搵去隻手結埋冰都搵唔到想食嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪間間都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩雪糕/雪條好推介？"},{"pid":"36cec6d4aa63011059972ee1d18dfd23f2e820a0","tid":123822,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"想食牛奶樂"},{"pid":"a734f3d253b189b87183517400490ced2e93528c","tid":123822,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"淨係食哈根大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其他好一般 又唔抵食"},{"pid":"aedefb19c10ce9be726bf9146ff97e2f6408fcbc","tid":123822,"uid":49275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"屌你地班仆街搵到成個雪糕櫃打仗咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f372f32d31fa6c7b4e99c8c48d5f7d0c71ddcbfa","tid":123822,"uid":79744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想食牛奶樂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牛奶樂正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但便利店都好似冇再賣<br />\n超市就冇留意"}]}